			<title>Prof. Ruth Panofsky: On the history, and collecting of, MacMillan Company of Canada</title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://traffic.libsyn.com/nigelbeale/Ruth_Panofsky_complete.mp3]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://hpcanpub.mcmaster.ca/files//imagecache/hpmedium/files/canpub/CP00225.jpg" alt="" width="286" height="393" /></p>
