<div><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">E</span></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">xtraordinary Canadians series. We met recently to talk about the vast disconnect between the work and the woman; depression, lesbianism and gaiety; about place, truth and memory, narrative and culture, confidence and role models.&nbsp;</span></span></div>
