            <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2522/3815370552_c16e62b6ec.jpg" alt="" width="281" height="375" /></p>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #333333;">established </span></span></span><span style="color: #333333;"><a href="http://www.greyweathers.com/Greyweathers%20Press%20Web/Pages/AboutThePress/aboutthepress.html"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">Greyweathers Press</span></span></a></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="color: #333333;"> </span><br /> </span></span></div>
<div style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2589/3814545077_8229162aa8.jpg" alt="" width="282" height="376" /><br /> </span></span></div>
