            <description><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3309/3508488552_5b91f5a1ba.jpg?v=0" alt="" width="280" height="372" /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><br /> </span></span></p>
