			<itunes:keywords>books,new,how,to,run,independent,craig,works,collected,bookstore,poile</itunes:keywords>

	<itunes:subtitle><![CDATA[
Listen here to my conversation with Craig Poile, co-owner of Collected Works, a successful, innovative independent bookstore based in Ottawa, Canada. We talk, among others things, about a rudimentary webcam-teleconferencing system dubbed &lsquo;Great Talking Head,&rsquo; that Craig has set up to get big name authors, such as Julian Barnes and Peter Carey, and their fans, together in his bookstore; about bookseller-publisher relations, in-store writing workshops and print-on-demand. ]]></itunes:subtitle>



