        <item>
			<title>Interview with Martin Levin, Books Editor at the Globe &amp; Mail Newspaper</title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://traffic.libsyn.com/nigelbeale/Matin_Levin_Globe_Books_Editor_Book_Expo_Canada_June_06.mp3]]></link>
